{"tid":2331704,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（反了反了）肉廠逾百中國員工就工作條件罷工「維權」","createTime":"2020-12-19T04:18:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-19T05:40:01.000Z","uid":54930,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"28cb28be53f4da63d86b93231d14ea977a35d4df","tid":2331704,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T04:18:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.sbs.com.au/language/cantonese/zh-hant/chinese-workers-return-to-work-in-warrnambool-after-employee-injured-in-altercation-at-abattoir\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sbs.com.au%2Flanguage%2Fcantonese%2Fzh-hant%2Fchinese-workers-return-to-work-in-warrnambool-after-employee-injured-in-altercation-at-abattoir&d=FaFb5890SAgm9tgOvLsHBTIStCm0mHK7%2Bbmf%2BnNiY0c%3D&h=cdf89f36\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.sbs.com.au/language/cantonese/zh-hant/chinese-workers-return-to-work-in-warrnambool-after-employee-injured-in-altercation-at-abattoir</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://sl.sbs.com.au/public/image/file/3cd7c438-a7a3-4e1a-a802-f14439659af1/crop/16x9_large\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsl.sbs.com.au%2Fpublic%2Fimage%2Ffile%2F3cd7c438-a7a3-4e1a-a802-f14439659af1%2Fcrop%2F16x9_large&h=0f410312&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《Weekly Times》報道，維州大型肉類加工廠Midfield集團位於Warrnambool的工廠，前日和昨日（12月16和17日）發生勞資糾紛。<br />\n據報道，該公司與一班持僱主擔保技術簽證（類別457）的中國工人，就工作條件和延長簽證問題產生磨擦。<br />\n今年較早前，聯邦政府更改簽證政策安排，在疫情期間容許從事關鍵行業的外勞延長居留12個月，這些行業包括肉類加工業。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n部份Midfield工人的簽證本來快將到期，受惠於新政策而獲延長到明年6月，但之後前景將不明確。<br />\n涉事的肉廠約有900名工人，其中大約150人是中國籍。據報道，部份中國工人希望申請永久居留簽證。<br />\n事件令工人和廠方關係緊張，一名工人與主管發生衝突。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://sl.sbs.com.au/public/image/file/c16dc3b9-9e1d-4cac-b35f-54f8beaac105\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsl.sbs.com.au%2Fpublic%2Fimage%2Ffile%2Fc16dc3b9-9e1d-4cac-b35f-54f8beaac105&h=a18a437c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n澳洲廣播公司報道，該名28歲王姓（音譯，Benson Wang）工人來自福建省，持有457簽證，5年前開始為Midfield打工，在衝突中造成腦震盪和眼眶瘀黑，送院治理。<br />\n<br />\n過去兩日，包括王在內的一批中國工人，在工廠停車場集合，說他們不滿廠方的處理手法。很多工人亦擔心他們的簽證即將到期。<br />\n《Weekly Times》報道，Midfield總經理Dean McKenn今日（12月18日）說，糾紛現已解決，工人將重新工作。他否認廠內工作文化欠佳，又認為有關簽證和永久居留權的決定，該由聯邦政府處理和釐清。<br />\n「他們想我們解決他們的簽證問題，但這不在我們控制範圍內。」<br />\n署理移民部長圖治（Alan Tudge）表示，當局在疫情期間已更改簽證安排，關鍵行業的臨時外勞可以延長居留12個月，包括肉類加工業，「這適用於Midfield集團，並已向一些工作發出了批准。」<br />\n「來自Midfield Meats或肉類行業的任何勞工協議申請，將按正常準則作評估。臨時簽證持有人可透過多個計劃申請永居簽證。除了這些簽證事宜，我不宜評論任何職場糾紛。」<br />\n曾與70名中國工人會面的澳洲肉類業僱員工會秘書Paul Conway表示，Midfield工廠裡勞資雙方有「深層問題」，不只是簽證問題，「我告訴70名工人明天回去上班，但還有很多事要跟這間公司解決，尤其是有關（上述打鬥事件和涉事者）。」"},{"pid":"ecffb9065dc09c87423b7f689ef4beed477cab2e","tid":2331704,"uid":129676,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T04:21:33.000Z","msg":"中國人都識罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69144e048e959f1a27a59e565b584d7bf0c432b5","tid":2331704,"uid":171107,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ecffb9065dc09c87423b7f689ef4beed477cab2e","tid":2331704,"uid":129676,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T04:21:33.000Z","msg":"中國人都識罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T04:24:24.000Z","msg":"香港人連支那人都不如<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qf0oUpq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqf0oUpq.jpg&h=94a9a845&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"02485a4de2ee7563dd175e72ec53731ee1a6de24","tid":2331704,"uid":2795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ecffb9065dc09c87423b7f689ef4beed477cab2e","tid":2331704,"uid":129676,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T04:21:33.000Z","msg":"中國人都識罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T05:06:28.000Z","msg":"人地罷左你唔信姐 因為得一次機會"},{"pid":"c784cff53e5ba0c9bc0680d81436d447afedf620","tid":2331704,"uid":18251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ecffb9065dc09c87423b7f689ef4beed477cab2e","tid":2331704,"uid":129676,"like":3,"dis